Prototype function body

dot-body.Rd

This should not be called directly, but is called from the API functions.

.body(
  memoised,
  fname,
  validators,
  endpoint,
  envWhere,
  isFile,
  raw,
  overwrite,
  file,
  async,
  .call
)

Arguments

memoised

Whether or not to memoise results
fname

The function name
validators

Validators for parameters
endpoint

Formatted endpoint URL
envWhere

Environment to evaluate in
isFile

Whether or not the endpoint is expect to return a file
raw

Whether to return JSON (TRUE) or data.table (FALSE)
overwrite

Whether or not to overwrite the file if @param file is specified
file

A filename to save results to
async

Whether or not to run asynchronously
.call

The original function call
